    @FullyTested
public abstract class BaseFixedSizeForwardingList<TValue>
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingList<TValue>
    This is a base class used by FixedSizeForwardingList and UnmodifiableForwardingList. There is no reason to use it directly; it is public only to expose documentation via Javadoc.
    Author:
    Kevin Connor ARPE (kevinarpe@gmail.com)
    See Also:
    FixedSizeForwardingList, UnmodifiableForwardingList, ForwardingList
